quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,7,"Ni gute ababangikanyamana bagirana amasezerano na Allah ndetse n’Intumwa ye, batari ba bandi mwagiranye amasezerano ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Ka’abat)? Igihe cyose bazabatunganira (bubahiriza amasezerano), namwe muzabatunganire (muyubahirize). Mu by’ukuri Allah akunda abamutinya"
  9,8,"Ni gute (mwagirana amasezerano nk’ayo na bo) kandi iyo babanesheje batita ku masano cyangwa amasezerano mwagiranye? Babagusha neza mu magambo gusa, nyamara imitima yabo itabyemera, kandi abenshi muri bo ni inkozi z’ibibi"
  9,9,"Baguranye amagambo ya Allah igiciro gito, banakumira (abantu kugana) inzira ye. Mu by’ukuri ibyo bakoraga ni bibi"
  9,10,(Abo babangikanyamana) ntibubahiriza isano cyangwa isezerano bafitanye n’umwemera! Kandi abo ni bo barengera (imbago za Allah)
  9,11,"Nibaramuka bicujije bagahozaho iswala, ndetse bakanatanga amaturo, ubwo bazaba babaye abavandimwe banyu mu idini. (Uko ni ko) dusobanura amagambo (yacu) ku bantu bafite ubumenyi"
  9,12,"Ariko nibatatira indahiro zabo nyuma y’amasezerano (mwagiranye) bakanasebya idini ryanyu, mujye murwanya abayobozi b’ubuhakanyi kugira ngo barekere aho (ibikorwa byabo bibi), kuko mu by’ukuri nta sezerano bajya bubahiriza"
  9,13,"Kuki mutarwanya abantu batatiye indahiro zabo bakanashaka kumenesha Intumwa (Muhamadi), kandi ari bo babashotoye bwa mbere? Ese murabatinya? Ahubwo Allah ni We mukwiye gutinya niba koko muri abemeramana"